	* smtp.el (smtp-send-buffer): Add DOC.
	(smtp-via-smtp): Add DOC.

	* FLIM-API.en (QMTP): Remove section.
	(smtp-send-buffer): Add description.
	(smtp-via-smtp): Likewise.


