	* mmgeneric.el (mime-insert-header-from-buffer): Rename
	field-presentation-mode `folding' to `wide'.

	* eword-decode.el: Rename field-presentation-modes from `native',
	`folding', `unfolding', `unfolding-xover' to `plain', `wide',
	`summary', `nov'.

